ohead]], [[Alanis Morissette]], [[Kid Rock]], [[Godsmack]], [[OutKast]], [[Reamonn]], [[Hed PE]], [[Mudvayne]], [[Neil Young]], [[Santana]], [[Journey (band)|Journey]], [[Iron Maiden]], [[Audioslave]], [[Evanescence]], [[Apocalyptica]], [[Judas Priest]], [[John Mayall]], [[3 Doors Down]], [[DanTDM|Daniel Middleton]], [[Nickelback]], [[Billy Idol]], [[Brian May]], [[Queens of the Stone Age]], [[Amy Winehouse]], [[Trivium (band)|Trivium]], [[36 Crazyfists]], [[Panic! at the Disco]] and [[Alice in Chains]].\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \n|}\n\n==2008 festival==\nThe 2008 festival took place on 6\u20138 June 2008. 91 acts have been officially confirmed. Both festivals were sold out on 1 May.\n\nConfirmed acts:\n<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rock-am-ring.de/newsitem.html?objId=21|title=Live - Rock am Ring 2017|website=Rock am Ring}}</ref>\n<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rock-am-ring.de/newsitem.html?objId=23|title=Live - Rock am Ring 2017|website=Rock am Ring}}</ref>\n<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rock-am-ring.de/newsitem.html?objId=24|title=Live - Rock am Ring 2017|website=Rock am Ring}}</ref>\n<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rock-am-ring.de/newsitem.html?objId=25|title=Live - Rock am Ring 2017|website=Rock am Ring}}</ref>\n<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rock-am-ring.de/newsitem.html?objId=27|title=Live - Rock am Ring 2017|website=Rock am Ring}}</ref>\n<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rock-am-ring.de/newsitem.html?objId=28|title=Live - Rock am Ring 2017|website=Rock am Ring}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"rock-am-ring.de\">{{cite web|url=http://www.rock-am-ring.de/newsitem.html?objId=29|title=Live - Rock am Ring 2017|website=Rock am Ring}}</ref>\n<br/>\n[[3 Doors Down]] (replacing [[Chris Cornell]], who backed out to record an album<ref name=\"rock-am-ring.de\"/>), [[36 Crazyfists]], [[Against Me!]], [[Airbourne (band)|Airbourne]], [[Alpha Galates]], [[Alter Bridge]], [[Animal Alpha]], [[Babyshambles]], [[Bad Religion]], [[Bedouin Soundclash]],