ript]], [[The Soundtrack of Our Lives]] (OEOC), [[The Subways]], [[Tomte (band)|Tomte]], [[Trivium (band)|Trivium]], [[Volbeat]], [[White Lies (band)|White Lies]]\nRock am Ring tickets were sold out by March 26.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rock-im-park.de/index.php?navi=1&rid=1&artid=583 |title=Live - Rock im Park 2016 |publisher=Rock-im-park.de |date= |accessdate=2016-06-04}}</ref>\n\n==2011 festival==\nThe headliners for the 2011 festival were [[System of a Down]], [[Coldplay]]. Other bands included [[Disturbed (band)|Disturbed]], [[Alter Bridge]], [[Rob Zombie]], [[Interpol (band)|Interpol]], [[Avenged Sevenfold]], [[Social Distortion]], [[Volbeat]], [[Beatsteaks]], [[August Burns Red]], [[The BossHoss]], [[Hurts]], [[Ko\u042fn]], [[Madsen (band)|Madsen]], [[Mando Diao]], [[The Kooks]], [[Sevendust]], [[In Flames]], [[3 Doors Down]], [[Lifehouse (band)|Lifehouse]], [[The Devil Wears Prada (band)|The Devil Wears Prada]], [[Ash (band)|Ash]] and [[The Gaslight Anthem]].\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| '''Center Stage (Rock am Ring)'''\n|-\n!Friday, 3\n!Saturday, 4\n!Sunday, 5\n|-\n|  style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:200px;\"|\n'''[[Kings of Leon]]'''<br />\n[[Mando Diao]]<br />\n[[Social Distortion]] <br />\n[[The Gaslight Anthem]] <br />\n[[Plain White T's]] <br />\n[[We Are Scientists]] <br />\n[[Thees Uhlmann| Thees Uhlmann & Band]] <br />\n|  style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:200px;\"|\n'''[[Coldplay]]'''<br />\n[[S\u00f6hne Mannheims]]<br />\n[[The Kooks]]<br />\n[[Hurts]]<br />\n[[Ash (band)|Ash]]<br />\n[[The Naked and Famous]] <br />\n[[Morning Parade]]<br />\n|  style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:200px;\"|\n'''[[System of a Down]]'''<br />\n[[Beatsteaks]]<br />\n[[Volbeat]]<br />\n[[Avenged Sevenfold]]<br />\n[[Hollywood Undead]]<br />\n[[Millencolin]]<br />\n[[Mastodon (band)|Mastodon]]<br />\n|}\n\n==2012 festival==\nActs for the 2012 edition included [